T02TD3203E:210a-1: s'i ta t'a ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD3203E:210a-3: sgrol ma dkar mo'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3203E:210a-4: zla ba drug tu sgrub pa la brtson pas //
T02TD3203E:210a-5: sgrol ma'i thugs kar 'khor lo bsgom pa la //
T02TD3203E:210a-6: 'chi bdag skyon gyis gos par 'gyur ma yin //
T02TD3203E:210a-7: dngos grub rnams kyang thams cad thob par 'gyur //
T02TD3203E:210a-8: 'chi ba slu ba bsdus pa las //
T02TD3203E:210a-9: sgrol ma dkar mo bton pa yi //
T02TD3203E:210a-10: bsgoms pas 'jigs pa sel byed pa'i //
T02TD3203E:210a-11: ngag gi dbang phyug gis 'di bya //
T02TD3203E:210a-12: sde bzhi dang po'i yig ldan las //
T02TD3203E:210a-13: 'od zer nam mkhar rnam spros pas //
T02TD3203E:210a-14: pad dkar zla ba'i gdan bltas la //
T02TD3203E:210a-15: mdun du gsum la skyabs 'gro brjod //
T02TD3203E:210a-16: rang bzhin sgro btags gzhom don du //
T02TD3203E:210a-17: stong pa nyid du yud tsam blta //
T02TD3203E:210a-18: de nas smon lam stobs las ni //
T02TD3203E:210a-19: byang chub sems kyi yi ge yin //
T02TD3203E:210a-20: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gdan steng na //
T02TD3203E:210a-21: rdo rje'i skyil krung legs par gnas //
T02TD3203E:210a-22: mchog sbyin ma dang autpala bsnams //
T02TD3203E:210a-23: ston ka'i zla ba ltar dkar zhing //
T02TD3203E:210a-24: rgyab ni zla ba la legs brten //
T02TD3203E:210a-25: lo ni bcu drug ma yi lus //
T02TD3203E:210a-26: rgyan rnams kun gyis legs brgyan ma //
T02TD3203E:210a-27: rdzogs sangs de dag thams cad sras //
T02TD3203E:210a-29: bsgoms la 'phags ma sgrol ma de'i //
T02TD3203E:210a-31: rtsibs brgyad la ni yi ge yang //
T02TD3203E:210a-32: brgyad kyis yongs su dgang bya ba //
T02TD3203E:210a-33: aom h'a gsal byed dbus gnas pa'i //
T02TD3203E:210b-0: bsgrub bya'i ming sogs @210b lte bar ni //
T02TD3203E:210b-1: bsgom bya rtse gcig sems kyis kyang //
T02TD3203E:210b-2: zla drug brtan pas nges bya zhing //
T02TD3203E:210b-3: sems skyon ni bzlas bya ba //
T02TD3203E:210b-4: sngags kyi yi ge bcu po 'di //
T02TD3203E:210b-5: aom gyi yi ge dang por sbyin //
T02TD3203E:210b-6: phyi nas t'a re legs par sbyar //
T02TD3203E:210b-8: de mtha' sv'a h'a las kun byed //
T02TD3203E:210b-9: tshangs dbang khyab 'jug nyi zla drug / phyogs skyod 'dod pa'i rgyal pos kyang //
T02TD3203E:210b-10: dgag par mi nus spu yi rtse //
T02TD3203E:210b-12: gnyer ma skra dkar skal ngan nad //
T02TD3203E:210b-13: dbul ba'ang kun nas zad par byed //
T02TD3203E:210b-14: seng ge la sogs 'jigs chen brgyad //
T02TD3203E:210b-15: sdug bsngal tshogs rnams 'jig par byed //
T02TD3203E:210b-16: gos skom khang bsangs rin chen sogs //
T02TD3203E:210b-17: btsal ba med par bde bar rnyed //
T02TD3203E:210b-18: ral gri mig rtsi rkang byug dang //
T02TD3203E:210b-19: bum pa bzang sogs dngos grub 'byung //
T02TD3203E:210b-20: yid gzhungs smra mkhas snyan dang dngags te //
T02TD3203E:210b-21: shes rab gcig tu dri med dang ;
T02TD3203E:210b-22: /'dod pa'i dngos grub gzhan rnams kyang //
T02TD3203E:210b-24: sgrol ma dkar mo'i sgrub thabs kyis //
T02TD3203E:210b-26: legs byung dge ba gang yin des //
T02TD3203E:210b-27: skye dgu sgrol ma nyid du shog / sgrol ma dkar mo'i sgrub thabs /
